## Order Service environment variables

# App port (optional)
PORT=3004

# MongoDB connection string
# - Local example: mongodb://localhost:27017/tomato_delivery
# - Atlas example: mongodb+srv://<user>:<pass>@<cluster-host>/<db>?retryWrites=true&w=majority
DATABASE_URL=

# Optional: fix MongoDB Atlas SRV DNS on some networks/ISPs
DNS_SERVERS=1.1.1.1,8.8.8.8

